{"id":"jabneh","term":"Jabneh","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Building, (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 26:6\">2 Chr. 26:6</a>), identical with Jabneel (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Joshua 15:11\">Josh. 15:11</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Chronicles 26:6","Joshua 15:11"]}